OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally dry to start, though
OL,6,Fthere could be some isolated showers
OL,7,Falong the coast in the early morning.
OL,8,FGood spells of sunshine through the
OL,9,Fmorning, though cloud may increase in
OL,10,Fthe afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FFine in the evening with
OL,13,Flight winds. A band of rain and low
OL,14,Fcloud moving in around midnight,
OL,15,Fcontinuing overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
